&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a fully remote Ad Build Specialist to support one of our biggest client accounts. This is an execution-focused role where speed, accuracy, and attention to detail are critical. You&#39;ll gain a deep fundamental understanding of how Meta Ads Manager works, including campaign, ad set, ad settings, how they impact delivery,spend and an advertisers overall performance in the digital ecosystem. We offer a full training program that covers the basics of what you will need to know, as well as additional optional sessions on other platforms, concepts and skills related to digital marketing&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities include, but are not limited to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build digital ads to specification across Meta and other advertising platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute high-volume ad creation requests with speed and accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow established naming conventions, campaign structures, and platform requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct quality assurance checks before launch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in training programs, including ad-platform-level training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with teammates to meet deadlines and support campaign launches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity for overtime pay at x rate based on client needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and commitment to accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable and able to follow established processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to learn quickly and adapt to new tools and workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interest in digital marketing and advertising&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No prior ad operations experience required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our interview process includes, but is not limited to the following:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excel, English and Typing Test&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
