&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Base salary DOE&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unlimited vacation policy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health insurance coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This is a remote role, but must be based in Colombia.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About WITHIN&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
