&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a fully remote Ad Operations Project Manager to oversee the end-to-end workflow for a high-volume ad build operation. This role is responsible for managing intake, prioritization, assignment, quality control, and launch readiness across a fast-moving queue of digital advertising projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll serve as the primary connection between account teams and ad builders, ensuring work is delivered accurately, efficiently, and on schedule.&lt;/p&gt;
