&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;The AI Creative Specialist is our go-to expert for leveraging cutting-edge generative AI in both imagery and video. You’ll utilize multiple AI tools and workflows—ranging from advanced prompt engineering to model training—to craft unique, high-quality visuals for our clients. As an integral part of our post-production and creative teams, you’ll push boundaries in AI-assisted content creation while ensuring outputs remain brand-consistent and commercially viable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities include but are not limited to;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced AI Model Utilization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertly employ various AI models (e.g., Stable Diffusion, Midjourney, DALL·E) and interfaces (ComfyUI or similar) to produce high-fidelity visuals and short-form video content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fine-tune, train, and adapt models for specialized product imagery, ensuring consistency with brand requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative Integration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Motion Graphics Designers, Video Editors, and Graphic Designers to embed AI-generated assets seamlessly into final deliverables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide teams on best practices for maximizing the potential of AI-generated components within larger creative campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Workflow Innovation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and refine processes for AI-driven content creation, including advanced prompt engineering and iterative workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on emerging AI technologies, identifying opportunities for the agency to adopt or pilot cutting-edge techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quality Assurance &amp;amp; Brand Consistency&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee quality checks on AI outputs, adjusting for color, composition, and brand alignment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure final deliverables meet both creative standards and client expectations across a variety of use cases (e.g., paid social, digital displays, print).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mentorship &amp;amp; Training&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance, tips, and training to junior team members interested in AI, sharing insights on prompt crafting, model selection, and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with team leads and project managers to assess project feasibility and timelines when incorporating AI-driven solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
