&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in SQL.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with cloud platforms (GCP, AWS, or Azure).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving skills and ability to debug complex system behavior.&lt;/li&gt;
