&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly motivated and experienced Email Marketing Coder to join our dynamic team. In this role, you will be responsible for developing and deploying email marketing campaigns across various internal systems, ensuring high-quality performance, and maintaining a strong adherence to industry best practices. You will work closely with the creative, marketing, and technical teams to bring designs to life and optimize campaigns for maximum effectiveness. Your expertise will play a key role in enhancing our email marketing efforts and contributing to the overall success of our digital strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
