&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quality Assurance &amp;amp; Troubleshooting:&lt;/strong&gt; Perform QA on HTML email files using tools such as Litmus, EmailOnAcid, or other similar inbox rendering tools. Troubleshoot and resolve any rendering or deliverability issues that arise during testing.&lt;/li&gt;
