&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Email Marketing Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 3 to 5 years of experience in the email marketing field, with a focus on email production, preferably using large enterprise email platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Proven ability to manage multiple projects and collaborate with internal stakeholders and partners. Strong client-service skills with an ability to manage expectations and deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Industry Knowledge:&lt;/strong&gt; Solid understanding of email technologies, best practices, and current trends. Ability to troubleshoot and optimize campaigns for performance and deliverability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Organizational Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; Excellent organizational skills with the ability to prioritize tasks and manage multiple campaigns and deadlines with minimal oversight.&lt;/li&gt;
