&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;The IT Manager will oversee daily IT operations, ensure the reliability and security of our systems, and lead support efforts across the organization. This role requires strong technical expertise, clear communication skills, and a highly proactive approach to both problem-solving and project execution. The ideal candidate anticipates issues before they arise, drives improvements, and takes full ownership of their work from start to finish.&lt;/p&gt;
